UP FAMNIT – Podatkovno programiranje/Data programming

Project Instructions/Navodila za projekt

May 2023

EN

There will not be any oral defenses of the projects.

The topic for your project must be on university level, made in Quarto. Pick a dataset among https://www.kaggle.com/datasets or similar database and study it. Use only methods, that lead to a solution, like user defined functions, mutate, filter, summarise, inner_join, ggplot, … Use the tidyverse approach by chaining the above functions and using pipes %>%. Show your mastery of R!

The project should include the following sections:

  1. Introduction / Presentation and description of the problem
  2. Presentation of the data (present the data by showing the head of your dataframes, showing the types and explaining what is column is/what unit is in.)
  3. Aggregation of data. Show the result as a table (at least 3)
  4. Exploratory data analysis ( Visualisation of the data, at least 3 relevant (and distinct) ggplots, that are not the same type of plot. Explain each ggplot)
  5. Interpretation / Conclusion
  6. References (at least of the location of the dataset. If you are reusing some text from wiki/book etc then reference it)

The project must be published online https://www.netlify.com/ (or https://student.famnit.upr.si/, …). Aside from this you must also submit it via e-classroom. Submit the .qmd file (and the necessary support files for rendering), .html file and .txt file with the name of the website, where it is published.

SLO

Ustnih zagovorov projektov ne bo.

Projekt po izbiri na univerzitetnem nivoju, izdelan s pomočjo Quarta. Izberite is dataset iz https://www.kaggle.com/datasets ali podobne podatkovne baze in ga preučite. Uporabite samo metode, ki bodo pripeljale k rešitvi, t.j. uporabniško definirane funkcije, mutate, filter, summarise, inner_join, ggplot, … Uporabite tidyverse pristop, kjer verižite zgornje funkcije z uporabo pipe %>%. Pokažite svoje obvladovanje R-ja!

Projekt naj vsebuje naslednja poglavja/točke:

  1. Uvod / Predstavitev in opis problema
  2. Predstavitev podatkov (predstavite podatke tako, da prikažete glavo svojih podatkovnih okvirov, prikažete vrste in razložite, kaj je stolpec/v kateri enoti je.)
  3. Agregacija podatkov. Prikaži izhodno tabelo (vsaj 3krat).
  4. Exploratory data analysis (Vizualizacija podatkov, vsaj 3 ustreznih (in različnih) ggplotov. Razložite vsak ggplot)
  5. Interpretacija / Zaključek
  6. Literatura / Reference (vsaj lokacija nabora podatkov. Če ponovno uporabljate nekaj besedila iz wiki/knjige itd., se nanj skličite)

Projekt morate objaviti preko spleta https://www.netlify.com/ (ali https://student.famnit.upr.si/, …). Poleg tega je projekte je potrebno oddati preko e-učilnice. Oddate .qmd datoteko (in ostale podporne datoteke), .html dokument in .txt datoteko z naslovom spletne strani na kateri ste objavili.

Netlify help

goto https://www.netlify.com/ and log in/register.

Rename your main .html file to “index.html”, drag the folder with it in the netlify app. The renaming is not optional and you must use the name “index.html”!

URL link to project: https://awesome-hawking-96d4b9.netlify.app
